data.title: Alex Chandon: Movies, Photos, Videos, News, Biography & Birthday
data.meta_description: Alex Chandon: Check out the list of all Alex Chandon movies along with photos, videos, biography and birthday. Also find latest Alex Chandon news on Times of India.
data.text:
'Broke PM Modi's confidence': Rahul Gandhi & Kharge vow statehood for J&K

timesofindia.com / Aug 22, 2024, 18:46 (IST)

Rahul Gandhi and Congress chief Kharge visit Jammu and Kashmir to drum up support and discuss alliances ahead of the upcoming elections. They promise to restore statehood, criticize PM Modi, and address the region's security issues, emphasizing Congress's role in safeguarding J&Kâ€™s land and people.

'Kolkata rape-murder scene altered, attempt to cover up': CBI to SC

timesofindia.com / Aug 22, 2024, 17:50 (IST)

The CBI informed the Supreme Court about a suspected cover-up in the Kolkata doctor rape and murder case, claiming crime scene tampering. The Bengal government denied this, asserting the process was recorded. Investigation hurdles stem from conflicting narratives. The Supreme Court earlier reproached authorities for delay in the FIR and mismanagement during a hospital protest.

Thailand reports Asia's first case of new Mpox strain

timesofindia.com / Aug 22, 2024, 18:48 (IST)

Thailand has identified its first case of the Mpox Clade 1b variant, found in a 66-year-old European man who travelled from Africa. This is the second instance of the strain detected outside Africa and the first in Asia. No local transmissions have been reported. Sweden previously recorded a case related to the African outbreak.

Cognizant India CMD Rajesh Nambiar resigns to join Indian IT's apex body

timesofindia.com / Aug 22, 2024, 01:27 (IST)

Nasscom appointed Rajesh Nambiar as its next President, to succeed Debjani Ghosh in November 2024. Nambiar, from Cognizant, will focus on AI, talent development, and IP creation in Indian tech.

Kamala, Mindy and a taste of India in US elections

tnn / Aug 22, 2024, 17:41 (IST)

Mindy Kaling's joke about Kamala Harris in a viral cooking video and her role in the Democratic convention highlight Harris' dual heritage. The event, reflecting America's diversity, included Hindu and Sikh delegates. Harris' culinary skills featured prominently, adding to her relatable persona.

'Nothing to do with financial returns': Olympian on quitting TT

timesofindia.com / Aug 22, 2024, 17:55 (IST)

Archana Kamath, an Indian table tennis player, is stepping away from elite sports to pursue a Master's in Public Policy at the University of Michigan. The 24-year-old Olympian prioritizes academics and plans to contribute to India's public policy sector after graduation, despite her successful sports career, including participation in the Paris Olympics.
